title: New York Rangers ( NHL ) average ticket price 2014/15
yAxis: Average ticket price in U.S. dollars
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Average ticket price in U.S. dollars, containing a total of 10 data points.
Overall Average ticket price in U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
Average ticket price in U.S. dollars is slightly increasing from 05/06 to 07/08, roughly constant from 07/08 to 10/11, and lastly slightly increasing from 10/11 to 14/15.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 10/11 and 11/12.
Maximum Average ticket price in U.S. dollars, about 77.87 was reported at Year 14/15
The lowest Average ticket price in U.S. dollars, of value 45.83 was reported at Year 05/06
